-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack boolball-0.6-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./boolball-0.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/boolball-0.6-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/boolball-0.6-X.tar.bz2

